    "data": [
        {
            "title": "佐敦男子車內暈倒揭吹波超標 涉酒後駕駛被捕",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/d3df4fab7e6e2bc86b47b2197faf1a2f/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250206/_2025020607032563867.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>佐敦發生醉駕案。今日（6日） 凌晨2時許，警方接獲報案，一輛私家車停泊於柯士甸道及彌敦道交界往紅磡方向，車內男司機懷疑暈倒。警員接報到場，發現男司機身上有酒氣。經初步調查，姓陳（30歲）男司機未能通過酒精呼氣測試，涉嫌酒後駕駛被捕。被捕男子已獲准保釋候查，須於三月上旬向警方報到。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2051090/即時-港聞-佐敦男子車內暈倒揭吹波超標-涉酒後駕駛被捕",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-06 07:10:50",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "西盃│盧比斯地頭再顯威風 巴塞新春有「蝠」同享",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"巴塞中場費明盧比斯曾在兩周前西甲主場與華倫西亞交手，個入攻入兩球。Reuters\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/2ef5cc56b26b2658f1a4d32ebab1ea19/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250205/_2025020520361120908.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">巴塞中場費明盧比斯曾在兩周前西甲主場與華倫西亞交手，個入攻入兩球。Reuters</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p></p><h3>足智彩球賽編號：FB7125<br/>\n華倫西亞 VS 巴塞隆拿<br/>\n香港時間周五凌晨4:30開賽<br/>\n推介：讓球[-1/-1.5]客勝</h3>\n<p>巴塞隆拿兩星期前曾在西甲主場7:1大勝華倫西亞，中場費明盧比斯在該役光芒四射，收錄2入球2助攻，成為蝙蝠軍的夢魘。恰巧兩軍今晚在西班牙盃8強再次碰頭，華倫西亞就算重返主場也好，但礙於聯賽護級形勢險峻料不會全力出擊，費明盧比斯可望再次重溫好夢，領軍躋身4強，一於捧讓球讓一球/球半「客勝」。\n\n</p>\n<p>過去2輪西甲全勝的巴塞，其中一輪正是在兩個星期前主場7:1大勝今場對手華倫西亞。巴塞在該仗已收起了羅拔利雲度夫斯基和柏迪等主力，派出費明盧比斯、法蘭基迪莊、費倫托利斯等副選出戰，仍然大勝而回，可見兩隊實力差距之大。更重要的是球隊今場預計再以副選陣容出戰，兩周前一仗有參考價值，費明盧比斯亦可望再做英雄。\n\n</p>\n<p>這名出身自拉馬西亞訓練營的自家青訓戰將，不僅在大勝華倫西亞時梅開二度，同時收錄2助攻，全場還有3次關鍵傳球、5次長傳、7次過人和1次攔截，表現八面玲瓏。此子心理佔盡上風，今場再鬥華倫西亞料繼續有高水準演出，領軍再大勝一場。\n\n</p>\n<p>搶攻打法讓得起\n\n</p>\n<p>主隊華倫西亞今季成績持續不振，現時在聯賽排19位，深陷降班漩渦，到最近面對皇家蘇斯達和切爾達都順利贏波，才取得寶貴6分，目前距離17位的愛斯賓奴只有4分，護級之途難得出現曙光。正因重燃護級希望，該隊若在今場西班牙盃跟實力有極大差距的巴塞隆拿搏命，可謂不設實際，倒不如留力在周日西甲對護級直接對手雷加利斯時搏命才是合理選擇，因此蝙蝠軍大有機會派遣後備兵上陣，兩隊在水平上的差距隨時進一步拉闊。\n\n</p>\n<p>巴塞要晉級應無難度可言，加上教練費歷克入主以來，球隊在領先下極少歎慢板，會繼續壓逼對手搶攻爭取大勝，故讓球盤讓一球/球半「客勝」絕對值得信任，有1.92倍捧得過。馬高\n\n</p><div id=\"gtx-trans\" style=\"position: absolute; left: -133px; top: -12px;\">\n<div class=\"gtx-trans-icon\"> </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2051050/即時-體育-西盃│盧比斯地頭再顯威風-巴塞新春有-蝠-同享",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-06 07:10:51",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "沙特聯│賓施馬復勇 豐「伊」足食買「和客」",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"伊蒂哈德隊長賓施馬今季表現大勇。Reuters\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/f7e015e2144378a19dbf3d220dae4fb2/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250205/_2025020520400356213.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">伊蒂哈德隊長賓施馬今季表現大勇。Reuters</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p></p><h3>足智彩球賽編號：FB7122<br/>\n艾塔亞文 VS 伊蒂哈德<br/>\nNow633台周五凌晨1:00直播<br/>\n推介：半全場「和客」</h3>\n<p>伊蒂哈德現時於沙特阿拉伯聯賽跟希拉爾同得46分排首次席，為重奪聯賽冠軍，在狀態大勇的射手兼隊長賓施馬帶領下，今晚作客艾塔亞文定當全力搶3分。不過考慮到主隊艾塔亞文防守力強，兩軍隨時到換邊後才分勝負，一於冷敲3.95倍的半全場「和客」。\n\n</p>\n<p>上季伊蒂哈德高調從皇家馬德里引入時任金球獎得主賓施馬，但最終卻衛冕聯賽失敗，後者全季各賽事上陣33次僅入16球，表現低於預期，隨即惹來外界批評。不過這名37歲法國射手今季顯然已進入狀態，17場所有比賽射入15球，還有5次助攻，表現大幅提升，包括一月份的5場賽事共入5球，今場面對在沙特聯排第9位的艾塔亞文，只要發揮水準應可取得士哥領軍全取3分。\n\n</p>\n<p>惟主場的艾塔亞文着重防守，今季18場聯賽只失16球，9次主場出擊更僅失7球，加上他們連續5場沙特聯於換邊前都保持不失，有條件在上半場守住伊蒂哈德，到下半場才分勝負。半全場「和客」值得捧場，半場和波2.21倍亦可以一試。馬高\n\n</p><div id=\"gtx-trans\" style=\"position: absolute; left: -110px; top: -12px;\">\n<div class=\"gtx-trans-icon\"> </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2051052/即時-體育-沙特聯│賓施馬復勇-豐-伊-足食買-和客",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-06 07:10:52",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "劉沛蘅呻相差9年演姐弟戀難投入  同ANSONBEAN拍咀戲險受傷丨獨家",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"劉沛蘅呻相差9年演姐弟戀難投入  同ANSONBEAN拍咀戲險受傷丨獨家\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/6a0b4e31b6fc4dbf487ae23edebb5e3d/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250206/_2025020600414083591.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">劉沛蘅呻相差9年演姐弟戀難投入  同ANSONBEAN拍咀戲險受傷丨獨家</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p><font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\"><font size=\"4\">33</font></font><font size=\"4\">歲劉沛蘅（</font><font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\"><font size=\"4\">Hillary</font></font><font size=\"4\">）和</font><font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\"><font size=\"4\">24</font></font><font size=\"4\">歲</font><font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\"><font size=\"4\">ANSONBEAN</font></font><font size=\"4\">（</font><font size=\"4\">陳毅燊</font><font size=\"4\">）在</font><font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\"><font size=\"4\">ViuTV</font></font><font size=\"4\">劇《老是常出現》，首演一對，還有咀嘴和床戲，但拍咀戲竟因大用力差點受傷，</font><font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\"><font size=\"4\">Hillary</font></font><font size=\"4\">又呻相差</font><font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\"><font size=\"4\">9</font></font><font size=\"4\">年姐弟戀難投入。而初次跟一班前輩合作，他們由緊張到得閒約飲茶，合作相當愉快。採訪</font><font size=\"4\">：</font><font size=\"4\">杜</font><font size=\"4\">杜 形象</font><font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\"><font size=\"4\">:</font><font size=\"4\">June Chow(Hillary) </font></font><font size=\"4\">髮型</font><font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\"><font size=\"4\">:Derek Li@Xenter Salon(ANSON)</font></font><font size=\"4\">、</font><font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\"><font size=\"4\">Seiko@hair culture(Hillary) </font></font><font size=\"4\">化妝</font><font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\"><font size=\"4\">:Zoe Fan(ANSON) </font></font><font size=\"4\">服裝</font><font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\"><font size=\"4\">:Dolce &amp; Gabbana(ANSON)</font></font><font size=\"4\">、</font><font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\"><font size=\"4\">Isabel Marant(Hillary)</font></font>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Hillary和ANSONBEAN外形合襯，完全看不出相差9歲。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/50b29cec3116e86b8538502b6d81814d/2025-02/IMG_4986.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Hillary和ANSONBEAN外形合襯，完全看不出相差9歲。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1943b30a0c07b3bee2ebbdcfa173f878/2025-02/IMG_4992.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/dd822c7c5e663cadb426be3ff432e11d/2025-02/IMG_4998.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ee9b562d6bd59dc9418791706b666f09/2025-02/IMG_5003.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p><font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\"><font size=\"4\">Hillary</font></font><font size=\"4\">和</font><font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\"><font size=\"4\">ANSONBEAN</font></font><font size=\"4\">雖然同公司，但合作演戲是首次，他們互讚對方是好對手，</font><font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\"><font size=\"4\">Hillary</font></font><font size=\"4\">很欣賞師弟的自律，「佢比較跳脫，好在意佢嘅外在，總之見到肌肉，佢開機前會做足準備，空檔會走去健身，幾勤力小弟弟。」</font><font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\"><font size=\"4\">ANSONBEAN</font></font><font size=\"4\">讚師姐口齒伶俐，思路清晰，「佢任何時候都非常有組識腦轉得好快，圍讀時一路讀一路調整個戲，睇得出非常專業。</font>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"單身的Hillary對姐弟戀頗抗拒，弟弟們冇機會了。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9b23dcff237b85320daae6359d0ca260/2025-02/IMG_4929.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        單身的Hillary對姐弟戀頗抗拒，弟弟們冇機會了。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"單身的Hillary對姐弟戀頗抗拒，弟弟們冇機會了。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d832b089d110d31c67604b3c8f7f6787/2025-02/IMG_4939.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        單身的Hillary對姐弟戀頗抗拒，弟弟們冇機會了。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"單身的Hillary對姐弟戀頗抗拒，弟弟們冇機會了。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5c4e0e3804f60c48cdb7a530d6a8a909/2025-02/IMG_4949.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        單身的Hillary對姐弟戀頗抗拒，弟弟們冇機會了。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"單身的Hillary對姐弟戀頗抗拒，弟弟們冇機會了。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8a64eab9c621db82a9bcdc361b466820/2025-02/IMG_4967.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        單身的Hillary對姐弟戀頗抗拒，弟弟們冇機會了。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"單身的Hillary對姐弟戀頗抗拒，弟弟們冇機會了。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a718638013fc7bc674f56ad406720a57/2025-02/IMG_4973.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        單身的Hillary對姐弟戀頗抗拒，弟弟們冇機會了。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"ANSONBEAN首拍喜劇好擔心，因難拿捏搞笑與現實界線。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/df210505766b5e6e3cb0278c44dd1104/2025-02/IMG_5008.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        ANSONBEAN首拍喜劇好擔心，因難拿捏搞笑與現實界線。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"ANSONBEAN首拍喜劇好擔心，因難拿捏搞笑與現實界線。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f89b91309c9dc407750443e115a5fe79/2025-02/IMG_5014.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        ANSONBEAN首拍喜劇好擔心，因難拿捏搞笑與現實界線。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p><font size=\"4\"><b>同前輩合作有壓力</b></font>\n</p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">劇中</font><font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\"><font size=\"4\">Hillary</font></font><font size=\"4\">跟</font><font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\"><font size=\"4\">ANSONBEAN</font></font><font size=\"4\">大談相差</font><font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\"><font size=\"4\">1</font></font><font size=\"4\">年姐弟戀，但現實</font><font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\"><font size=\"4\">Hillary</font></font><font size=\"4\">大足</font><font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\"><font size=\"4\">9</font></font><font size=\"4\">歲，她坦承好難投入，特別是兩人的咀嘴戲，比起拍另一場床戲更困難，「我唔係幾接受到姐弟戀，抽離咗個角色當佢好似細佬咁，佢又係師弟，感覺上保護去湊住佢，要拍呢場戲有啲怪怪的，比起場搞笑嘅床戲，呢場反而難投入。」她拍這場戲還差點受傷，「佢係強吻我，一攬埋嚟就錫，撞到我面容扭曲，拍咗幾次都牙撞嘴唇好痛。」</font><font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\"><font size=\"4\">ANSONBEAN</font></font><font size=\"4\">就解釋事前不用向女友張天穎備案，「套劇係</font><font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\"><font size=\"4\">2022</font></font><font size=\"4\">年</font><font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\"><font size=\"4\">8</font></font><font size=\"4\">月拍，嗰時未識，但將來要拍都會講聲，尊重嚟。」</font>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Hillary反而認為跟ANSONBEAN的床戲，比咀戲更易應付。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2068e4bdb910451d081ea7c76b72fa68/2025-02/12_6.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Hillary反而認為跟ANSONBEAN的床戲，比咀戲更易應付。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Hillary笑言對住ANSONBEAN，戲裏戲外都似湊細佬。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5ad72a3c4e508a37e6df8a1f64dc809e/2025-02/14_3.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Hillary笑言對住ANSONBEAN，戲裏戲外都似湊細佬。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"ANSONBEAN拍咀戲前，會向女友張天穎備案以示尊重。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/31261f4a70841282c55302c0559313dd/2025-02/WNE02P04261124.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        ANSONBEAN拍咀戲前，會向女友張天穎備案以示尊重。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">講到初次跟一班前輩合作，兩人難免會緊張，</font><font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\"><font size=\"4\">Hillary</font></font><font size=\"4\">說：「開頭未熟，劉老師（劉江）唔笑個樣又幾嚴肅，好驚佢哋覺得我唔專業，係啲壓力，但之後大家對戲有商有量，食飯佢哋又會講吓以前點拍嘢，氣氛緩和晒。」</font><font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\"><font size=\"4\">ANSONBEAN</font></font><font size=\"4\">更跟前輩「打」一片，「雷哥（張雷）有好多故事，會同我分享玩電單車，又會騷吓佢啲武功，我哋得閒仲會約飲茶，拍攝時好多謝各位前輩畀個好舒服嘅環境畀我哋去演。」</font>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Hillary和ANSONBEAN都認為張雷是前輩中最跳皮。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5cf7caf538e41a32187a2eb7b3666cb2/2025-02/2_15.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Hillary和ANSONBEAN都認為張雷是前輩中最跳皮。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Hillary開心過年後「6膠」再合作，最期待可以到海外拍。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/644aef10871542fd39cd212127f3a27d/2025-02/01_1_4.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Hillary開心過年後「6膠」再合作，最期待可以到海外拍。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
