        {
            "title": "天文台｜今日早上清涼 下午短暫時間有陽光及乾燥 最高氣溫約18度",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"黎志偉攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/b59a272ac738ca3d940bdfe8ea8515ca/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250206/_2025020606295492899.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">黎志偉攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>一股偏東氣流正影響廣東沿岸。同時，一道雲帶覆蓋該區。\n\n</p>\n<p>本港地區今日天氣預測，大致多雲。早上清涼，有一兩陣微雨。下午短暫時間有陽光及乾燥，最高氣溫約18度。吹和緩至清勁東至東北風。\n\n</p>\n<p>展望明日漸轉吹偏北風，氣溫逐步下降。週末期間早上寒冷，市區最低氣溫在11度左右，新界再低幾度，天色逐漸好轉，日間非常乾燥。星期一早上氣溫仍然較低。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4062131/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"分區氣溫\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2dcbb2b799ee099f519f4f6d3bc58f61/2025-02/2025-02-06_06_23_22.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        分區氣溫\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4062132/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"九天天氣預報\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/75aa5bd18116c0edcabd26d4b2ae8e1a/2025-02/2025-02-06_06_23_44.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        九天天氣預報\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4062133/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"今日早上清涼。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8108a11bcef1fd3e5355554e12a9034c/2025-02/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-02-06-06-21-38_003.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        今日早上清涼。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4062134/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"下午短暫時間有陽光及乾燥。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/08100d910dbf584e5da4f5f0fd4ec5f5/2025-02/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-02-06-06-21-41_004.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        下午短暫時間有陽光及乾燥。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4062135/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"最高氣溫約18度。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/cea39b01fd3717ce8c3a145747cb66aa/2025-02/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-02-06-06-21-44_005.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        最高氣溫約18度。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>一股偏東氣流會在今日影響廣東沿岸，同時一道雲帶會覆蓋該區。而一股強烈冬季季候風會在明日抵達華南沿岸，週末期間該區早上寒冷，內陸地區嚴寒，華南漸轉天晴乾燥。隨著季候風在下週初被偏東氣流取代，下週中期廣東沿岸氣溫逐步回升，天氣較為潮濕。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
